page.title: 17Barkestone wild flowers
page.content: These are some of the wild flowers that grow in Plungar Barkestone and Redmile.The dandelion,a yellow flower with lots of tiny petals,it grows near hedges and in fields.Hedge parsley,from the parsley family,has white flowers that are very small and in clusters.The hawthorn has a pinky white flower and has berries and is found in hedges.Squinancy wort has a white flower and a thin stem and bits sticking out of it.The daisy is a white flower that sometimes has pink underneath it.It is small.The buttercup is a yellow flower which has shiny petals.It can grow very tall.This is a list of some of the other plants:clover,field speedwell,field poppy,dock,hairy tare and red clover.
